Package: slcr
Title: Interface to Altair SLC from R
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Author: Michael Mayer [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Michael Mayer <michael.mayer@posit.co>
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Mayer", email = "michael.mayer@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an R interface to Altair SLC, enabling users to execute SLC 
    code and transfer data between R and SLC environments. This package offers 
    functionality similar to the 'sasquatch' package but uses Altair SLC instead 
    of SAS.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
SystemRequirements: Altair SLC (>= 2026)
Imports:
    reticulate
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    mockery,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/quarto/extension: slcr
